OL,5, When Mark Murray tells Pope Francis of 
OL,6, the sexual abuse he suffered as a child
OL,7, at a Catholic priest training school,  
OL,8, he just wants the Pope to listen.      
OL,10,FMr Murray is one of seven sexual abuse 
OL,11,Fsurvivors from St Peter Claver College 
OL,12,Fin West Yorkshire who will meet the    
OL,13,FPope in private on Monday morning.     
OL,15,FHe endured repeated abuse by a priest  
OL,16,Fat the former junior seminary between  
OL,17,F1969, when he joined aged 13, and 1974.
OL,19,F"I don't want an apology, I want them  
OL,20,Fto listen to me," said Mr Murray, 65.  
